Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-rolling-laser-geometry, ros-rolling-launch, ros-rolling-launch-ros, ros-rolling-message-filters, ros-rolling-rclcpp, ros-rolling-rclcpp-components, ros-rolling-sensor-msgs, ros-rolling-tf2, ros-rolling-tf2-ros, ros-rolling-tf2-sensor-msgs, ros-rolling-ros-workspace
Description: Converts a 3D Point Cloud into a 2D laser scan.
 This is useful for making devices like the Kinect appear like a laser scanner for 2D-based algorithms (e.g. laser-based SLAM).
